# LinkedIn Article – Day 02

## Title:
BubuVerse Tokenomics Model: Designed for Long-Term Value Creation

## Summary:
In this LinkedIn post, I analyze how BubuVerse’s tokenomics model is structured for long-term sustainability.  
It explains how the use of Starlight Energy, guild progression, and NFT evolution together create an economy where players, not just early investors, benefit from consistent engagement.

